1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
What if a tiny change could reshape an entire species?

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
This is the bottleneck effect, a crucial concept in evolution.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:11,600
When a population's size drastically reduces, genetic diversity plummets.

4
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:15,600
Imagine a forest fire wiping out most of a species.

5
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:17,600
Surviving members have fewer genes.

6
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:21,600
This can lead to inbreeding and reduced resilience against diseases.

7
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:23,200
It's a genetic gamble.

8
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:26,000
Want to dive deeper into evolutionary science?

9
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:27,600
Hit subscribe for more!
